column2: Perceives independence and the ability to organize personal life, although self-centered tendencies may occasionally arise. Significant factors in this quadrant highlight the areas designated for self-expression.
Receptive to others and sensitive to the subtle dynamics inherent in interpersonal relationships.
Seeks relationships from an objective standpoint rather than a personal one and values public engagement alongside contributing to society.
Strives to make a distinct mark on the world. While this ambition can be beneficial, an overemphasis on idealistic pursuits may become disruptive.
